OL,3,CScientists use lab-grown 'mini guts'
OL,4,Cto study Crohn's disease
OL,6,FIn the new research, published in Gut,
OL,7,Fthe researchers used cells from
OL,8,Finflamed guts, donated by 160 people,
OL,9,Fmainly patients and adolescents, but
OL,10,Falso healthy people, at CUH to grow
OL,11,Fmore than 300 mini-guts.
