OL,3,CScientists use lab-grown 'mini guts'
OL,4,Cto study Crohn's disease
OL,6,FThe study found that these changes in
OL,7,FCrohn's patients correlated with
OL,8,Fseverity of disease.
OL,10,FArthur Hatt, 11, was was diagnosed
OL,11,Fwith Crohn's at the age of nine and
OL,12,Fhas donated some of the cells from his
OL,13,Fintestine to the study.
OL,15,FHe said: "I think it's quite cool to
OL,16,Fbe part of the study.
OL,18,F"It's nice to know they're trying to
OL,19,Fget more information about Crohn's."
