OL,6,FHis mother, Sian Hatt, said there were
OL,7,Ftimes when Arthur was able to attend
OL,8,Fschool only for half days, and that
OL,9,Feven now holidays tend to be about
OL,10,Fgetting rest.
OL,12,FArthur particularly suffers during
OL,13,Fcold andseason, as the treatments also
OL,14,Ftend to suppress the immune system.
OL,16,FThe research was largely supported by
OL,17,Fthe Medical Research Council, and was
OL,18,Falso supported through collaboration
OL,19,Fwith the Milner Therapeutics
OL,20,FInstitute, University of Cambridge.
